<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Seascope Glass Boat</title>
    <style>
        .back{
            font-size: 27px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: black;
        }
        .paragraph{
            font-size: 25px;
        }
        .back:hover{
            color: rgb(37, 37, 37);
        }
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .paragraph{
                font-size: 25px;
                width: 280vw;
            }
        }
        .translation-btn-usa{
            position: absolute;
            height: 50px;
            width: 50px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            cursor: pointer;
            margin-top: -80px;
            margin-left: 1300px;
        }
        .translation-btn-ro{
            position: absolute;
            height: 50px;
            width: 50px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            cursor: pointer;
            margin-top: -80px;
            margin-left: 1390px;
        }
        .invisible{
            display: none;
            top: -1000000px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <a class="back" href="/marsalam/home">     <p class="back">←</p>    </a>
    <div class="translation">
        <img src="/images/1200px-Flag_of_the_United_States.svg.png" class="translation-btn-usa" id="translation-btn-usa">
        <img src="/images/1200px-Flag_of_Romania.svg.png" class="translation-btn-ro" id="translation-btn-ro">
    </div>
    <h1>Seascope Glass Boat</h1>
    <p id="paragraph-ro" class="paragraph">
        Este o oferta perfecta pentru oamenii care isi doresc sa vada recifele uimitoare. Privitul vietii de sub apa este posibil multumita magnificului geam de pe puntea inferioara a barcii
        Puntea inferioara are aer conditionat si se poate scufunda aproximativ 2-3 metri adancime pentru o privelistea subacvatica mai clara. Barca pleaca din Portul Ghalib.
        Echipajul de la bordul vasului sunt vorbitori de engleza . Bauturile nonalcoolice sunt incluse. Plecare de la hotel este dupa micul dejun, iar sosirea va fi în jurul  prânzului.
        <br><br>
        Adult: 70 €<br>
        Copil: 35 €<br><br>
        Cand:<br>
        in fiecare zi
    </p>
    <p id="paragraph-usa" class="paragraph invisible">
        It is a perfect offer for people who wish to see amazing reefs. Watching underwater life is possible thank 
        to magnifying glass on the side of boat from lower deck. The lower deck is air-conditioned and dove at 
        about 2-3m depth to make the underwater view clearly visible. Boat takes off from Port Ghalib. English 
        speaking crew on the boat and non alcoholic drinks included. Departure from hotel after breakfast, arrival
        for lunch
        <br><br>
        When:<br>
        Every day
    </p>
</body>
<script>
    const translateBtnUsa = document.getElementById("translation-btn-usa")
    const translateBtnRo = document.getElementById("translation-btn-ro")
    const paragraphUsa = document.getElementById("paragraph-usa")
    const paragraphRo = document.getElementById("paragraph-ro")

    translateBtnUsa.addEventListener("click", ()=>{
        paragraphUsa.classList.remove("invisible")
        paragraphRo.classList.add("invisible")
    })

    translateBtnRo.addEventListener("click", ()=>{
        paragraphUsa.classList.add("invisible")
        paragraphRo.classList.remove("invisible")
    })

</script>
</html>